beer_name: Brutal Brewing Pistonhead Hot Roddin Lager

review_blob: A good beer. Fits to food or just to drink it as it is.
Not so good. Tasted a bit like water to me.
This is not as good as Haake-Beck Pils. I think theres to much alcohol in this one.
This is a really fresh beer. The can is fun to.
No thanks. At least not if I can get anything better. The metallic taste is just to much.
This one makes me feel sick. It looks quite good, but thats all.
Not my kind of beer. It is nice with the black colour, but I can not drink a lot of this one, or I will vomit.
Honestly this is one of the worst beers I know. Make me feel sick. The only good with this beer is that it is a little taste and not just water.
Tastes good, a little bit like candy. The bottle looks really fresh and makes you feel happy.
I like this one. It is fresh and tastes good on a warm summerday. The bottle looks ok to.
I expected much from this beer. But it was not what I wanted. Was from time to time like water.
This is not the best beer I know. But it is however better than most of the swedish beers. Fits to crisps.
Without hesitation the best beer I know. Unfortunately you can only find this in Bremen.
This is one of the best beers in the world. I like the bottle a lot while it looks so fresh. This beer fits to every moment.
